    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            55,
            132,
            144,
            147
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $x - 3y - z + 4 = 0.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            154,
            334,
            168
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 显然所求平面的法向量为 $n = \\{-1,3,1\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            175,
            495,
            190
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所求平面为 $-(x - 1) + 3(y - 2) + (z + 1) = 0$ ，即 $x - 3y - z + 4 = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            196,
            690,
            211
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\mathrm{e}^{2a}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            217,
            194,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left(\\frac{x + a}{x - a}\\right)^x = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left[\\left(1 + \\frac{2a}{x - a}\\right)^{\\frac{x - a}{2a}}\\right]^x\\cdot \\frac{2a}{x - a} = \\mathrm{e}^{2a}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            240,
            568,
            275
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】1.",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            280,
            181,
            297
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f[f(x)] = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}1, & |f(x)|\\leqslant 1,\\\\ 0, & |f(x)| > 1. \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            302,
            400,
            338
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $|f(x)| \\leqslant 1$ ，所以 $f[f(x)] = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            344,
            409,
            360
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{2}\\left(1 - \\frac{1}{\\mathrm{e}^4}\\right)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            367,
            280,
            396
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 改变积分次序得",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            403,
            285,
            420
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\int_ {0} ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\int_ {x} ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y \\int_ {0} ^ {y} \\mathrm {d} x = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} y \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} y = - \\frac {1}{2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- y ^ {2}} \\left| _ {0} ^ {2} = \\frac {1}{2} \\left(1 - \\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {4}}\\right). \\right.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            194,
            424,
            820,
            456
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】2.",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            464,
            183,
            479
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\mathbf{A} = (\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}^{\\mathrm{T}},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{4}^{\\mathrm{T}}) = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 2 & 3 & 4 & 5\\\\ 3 & 4 & 5 & 6\\\\ 4 & 5 & 6 & 7 \\end{bmatrix} \\rightarrow \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 0 & -1 & -2 & -3\\\\ 0 & -2 & -4 & -6\\\\ 0 & -3 & -6 & -9 \\end{bmatrix} \\rightarrow \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4\\\\ 0 & 1 & 2 & 3\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 & 0 \\end{bmatrix},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            484,
            826,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $r(\\mathbf{A}) = 2$ ，所以该向量组的秩为2.",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            569,
            413,
            585
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            55,
            591,
            144,
            607
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 (A).",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            612,
            204,
            627
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $F^{\\prime}(x) = f(\\mathrm{e}^{-x})(\\mathrm{e}^{-x})^{\\prime} - f(x) = -\\mathrm{e}^{-x}f(\\mathrm{e}^{-x}) - f(x)$ ，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            633,
            688,
            650
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 (A).",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            656,
            204,
            670
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由 $f^{\\prime}(x) = [f(x)]^{2}$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            676,
            342,
            692
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x) = 2 f (x) f ^ {\\prime} (x) = 2 [ f (x) ] ^ {3}, \\\\ f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x) = 2 \\times 3 [ f (x) ] ^ {2} f ^ {\\prime} (x) = 3! [ f (x) ] ^ {4}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            167,
            697,
            555,
            735
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由归纳法得 $f^{(n)}(x) = n!\\left[f(x)\\right]^{n + 1}$ ，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            739,
            485,
            756
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            762,
            204,
            777
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $\\left|\\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2}\\right| \\leqslant \\frac{1}{n^2}$ 且 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{1}{n^2}$ 收敛，所以 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2}$ 绝对收敛；",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            782,
            654,
            816
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}$ 发散，所以 $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\left(\\frac{\\sin n\\alpha}{n^2} -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right)$ 发散，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            822,
            553,
            856
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            864,
            204,
            878
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{1 - \\cos{x}} = 2$ ，所以由极限保号性，存在 $\\delta >0$ ，当 $0 < |x| < \\delta$ 时， $\\frac{f(x)}{1 - \\cos{x}} >0.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            885,
            894,
            912
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $1 - \\cos x > 0$ ，所以 $f(x) > 0 = f(0)$ ，故 $x = 0$ 为极小值点，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            919,
            719,
            936
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 （B）.",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            67,
            210,
            82
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】令 $k_{1}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + k_{2}(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} - \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}) = \\mathbf{0}$ ，即 $(k_{1} + k_{2})\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} - k_{2}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\mathbf{0}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            89,
            623,
            105
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2}$ 线性无关，所以 $k_{1} + k_{2} = 0, - k_{2} = 0$ ，或 $k_{1} = 0,k_{2} = 0$ ，即 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}$ 线性无关，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            110,
            880,
            125
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又因为 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}$ 为齐次线性方程组 $AX = 0$ 的解，所以 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}$ 为齐次线性方程组 $AX = 0$ 的基础解系；",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            132,
            935,
            165
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $\\frac{\\pmb{\\beta}_1 + \\pmb{\\beta}_2}{2}$ 为非齐次线性方程组 $AX = b$ 的解，故 $k_{1}\\alpha_{1} + k_{2}(\\alpha_{1} - \\alpha_{2}) + \\frac{\\pmb{\\beta}_{1} + \\pmb{\\beta}_{2}}{2}$ 为 $AX = b$ 的通解，应选(B).三、",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            175,
            933,
            226
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】 $\\int_0^1\\frac{\\ln(1 + x)}{(2 - x)^2}\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_0^1\\ln (1 + x)\\mathrm{d}\\left(\\frac{1}{2 - x}\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            235,
            475,
            262
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} = \\left. \\frac {\\ln (1 + x)}{2 - x} \\right| _ {0} ^ {1} + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\frac {1}{(x - 2) (x + 1)} d x \\\\ = \\ln 2 + \\frac {1}{3} \\ln \\left| \\frac {x - 2}{x + 1} \\right| _ {0} ^ {1} = \\ln 2 - \\frac {2}{3} \\ln 2 = \\frac {1}{3} \\ln 2. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            235,
            696,
            338
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【解】 $\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = 2f_1' + y\\cos x \\cdot f_2'$ ,",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            348,
            371,
            374
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x \\partial y} = 2 \\left(- f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\sin x \\cdot f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) + \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} + y \\cos x \\left(- f _ {2 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\sin x \\cdot f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) \\\\ = - 2 f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + (2 \\sin x - y \\cos x) \\cdot f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} + y \\sin x \\cos x \\cdot f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            97,
            384,
            719,
            435
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【解】 特征方程为 $\\lambda^2 + 4\\lambda + 4 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\\lambda_1 = \\lambda_2 = -2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            443,
            607,
            457
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = (C_1 + C_2x)\\mathrm{e}^{-2x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            464,
            514,
            479
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{-2x}$ 的特解为 $y_0(x) = ax^2\\mathrm{e}^{-2x}$ ，代入得 $a = \\frac{1}{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            489,
            661,
            514
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $y^{\\prime \\prime} + 4y^{\\prime} + 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{-2x}$ 的通解为",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            522,
            373,
            538
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\ny = (C _ {1} + C _ {2} x) \\mathrm {e} ^ {- 2 x} + \\frac {1}{2} x ^ {2} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- 2 x} (C _ {1}, C _ {2} \\text {为 任 意 常 数}).\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            289,
            547,
            739,
            573
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、【解】 由 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = 1$ 得幂级数的收敛半径 $R = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            582,
            533,
            614
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x = \\pm 1$ 时， $(2n + 1)(\\pm 1)^n \\to \\infty (n \\to \\infty)$ ，即 $x = \\pm 1$ 时，幂级数发散，",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            621,
            706,
            634
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故幂级数的收敛域为 $(-1, 1)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            643,
            334,
            656
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $S(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}(2n+1)x^{n}$ ,",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            666,
            322,
            695
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $S(x) = 2x\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}nx^{n - 1} + \\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}x^{n} = 2x(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}x^{n})^{\\prime} + \\frac{1}{1 - x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            702,
            559,
            733
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= 2 x \\left(\\frac {x}{1 - x}\\right) ^ {\\prime} + \\frac {1}{1 - x} = \\frac {1 + x}{(1 - x) ^ {2}}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            167,
            742,
            471,
            767
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】 方法一",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            61,
            777,
            210,
            791
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $\\Sigma_0: z = 0 (x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 4)$ ，取下侧，",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            796,
            390,
            811
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nI = \\iint_ {\\Sigma + \\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y - \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            316,
            818,
            714,
            854
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $\\iint_{\\Sigma + \\Sigma_0} yz \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + 2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = \\iiint_{\\Omega} z \\, \\mathrm{d}v = \\int_0^{2\\pi} \\, \\mathrm{d}\\theta \\int_0^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}} \\, \\mathrm{d}\\varphi \\int_0^2 r^3 \\sin \\varphi \\cos \\varphi \\, \\mathrm{d}r$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            861,
            611,
            897
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\sin \\varphi \\cos \\varphi d \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {2} r ^ {3} d r = 4 \\pi ;\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            289,
            905,
            572,
            932
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = - 2 \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 4} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = - 8 \\pi ,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            105,
            67,
            592,
            107
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $I = 12\\pi$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            110,
            185,
            125
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            132,
            146,
            146
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nI = \\iint_ {\\Sigma} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iint_ {\\Sigma} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x + 2 \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            309,
            150,
            708,
            186
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令曲面 $\\Sigma$ 位于 $xOz$ 平面右侧的部分为 $\\Sigma_{1}$ ，由对称性得",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            189,
            528,
            204
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\iint_ {\\Sigma} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x = 2 \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {1}} y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x = 2 \\iint_ {D _ {x z}} z \\sqrt {4 - x ^ {2} - z ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x \\\\ = 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\mathrm {d} \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {2} r ^ {2} \\sin \\theta \\cdot \\sqrt {4 - r ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} r = 4 \\int_ {0} ^ {2} r ^ {2} \\sqrt {4 - r ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} r \\\\ \\frac {r = 2 \\sin t}{4} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} 4 \\sin^ {2} t \\cdot 4 \\cos^ {2} t d t = 6 4 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} (\\sin^ {2} t - \\sin^ {4} t) d t \\\\ = 6 4 \\left(\\frac {1}{2} \\cdot \\frac {\\pi}{2} - \\frac {3}{4} \\cdot \\frac {1}{2} \\cdot \\frac {\\pi}{2}\\right) = 4 \\pi ; \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            177,
            211,
            725,
            352
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n2 \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = 2 \\iint_ {D _ {x y}} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = 2 \\times 4 \\pi = 8 \\pi ,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            360,
            400,
            399
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $I = \\iint_{\\Sigma} yz \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + 2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = 12\\pi.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            401,
            369,
            434
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "六、【证明】因为 $f(x)$ 不恒为常数，且 $f(a) = f(b)$ ，所以存在 $c \\in (a, b)$ ，使得 $f(c) \\neq f(a)$ ，不妨设 $f(c) > f(a)$ ，由拉格朗日中值定理，存在 $\\xi \\in (a, c) \\subset (a, b)$ ，使得",
